    "content_license" : "CC BY-SA 4.0",
    "body" : "<p>In my case I had to remove some files that were created by gradle at some point in my study to make things work. So, cleaning up after messing up and then it ran fine ...</p>\n\n<p>If you experienced this issue in a git project, do <code>git status</code> and remove the unrevisioned files. (For me <code>elasticsearch</code> had a problem with <code>plugins/analysis-icu</code>).</p>\n\n<p><code>Gradle Version</code>        : 5.1.1</p>\n"
