    "last_activity_date" : 1710312741,
    "creation_date" : 1710312741,
    "answer_id" : 78151732,
    "question_id" : 23796404,
    "content_license" : "CC BY-SA 4.0",
    "body" : "<p>I met the same issue:</p>\n<p>It was because of gradle version, <code>compile</code> command is expired and was replaced by <code>api/implementation</code>, and In gradle 7.0+, it was removed.</p>\n<p>I still want to use <code>compile</code>, so I downgrade gradle version to gradle 4.10.</p>\n<p>In file <code>gradle-wrapper.properties</code>, use  <code>distributionUrl=https\\://services.gradle.org/distributions/gradle-4.10.3-all.zip</code></p>\n"
  } ],
